## Development

### Prerequisites

- [Rust](https://rustup.rs/) (latest stable version)

### Building

```bash
cargo build
```

### Testing

```bash
# Run all tests
cargo test

# Run tests with output
cargo test -- --nocapture

# Run specific test
cargo test test_hello
```

### Benchmarking

```bash
cargo bench
```

### Documentation

```bash
# Generate and open documentation
cargo doc --open

# Test documentation examples
cargo test --doc
```

### Linting

```bash
# Check formatting
cargo fmt --check

# Run clippy
cargo clippy -- -D warnings
```

